The deep denoising autoencoder for signal enhancment and representation [1]

Training Step
Train_Step('TrainPink0dB.list', 'TrainClean.list', 80, [400 400 400], 30);
argv[1] - Input training noisy speech list
argv[2] - Input training clean speech list
argv[3] - Feature dimension 
argv[4] - DDAE strucutre
argv[5] - Number of training iterations

Testing Step
Test_Step ('IntputPink0dB.list','OutPink0dB.list', 'Mel_1_BS5000_PN80000_epoch30_HS400_HS400_HS400_MHINT.mat', [400 400 400], 80);
argv[1] - Input testing noisy speech list
argv[2] - Output enhanced speech list
argv[3] - DDAE model
argv[4] - DDAE strucutre
argv[5] - Feature dimension 


